getContract
===========

Returns the details of the contract at the specified address

-------
Usage
-------

.. code-block:: javascript

  tronWeb.trx.getContract(contractAddress);

--------------
Parameters
--------------

String

-------
Returns
-------

Object

-------
Example
-------

.. code-block:: javascript

  >tronWeb.trx.getContract("TEEXEWrkMFKapSMJ6mErg39ELFKDqEs6w3").then(console.log)
